features: The La Newborn Boutique is a realistically looking ANATOMICALLY CORRECT REAL GIRL newborn doll that perfectly captures bringing a baby home from the nursery. The doll has a soft and adorable face with bright happy eyes and irresistibly cute crinkly toes.

The La Newborn Boutique baby doll comes with an 9-piece GIFT SET for dress-up fun. This includes: 1 short-sleeve baby shirt, 1 diaper cover, 1 pair of booties, 1 hat, 1 cloth diaper, 1 Soft Blanket, Belly Button Gauze, 1 hospital bracelet and Birth Certificate.

The doll’s jointed at the shoulders, hips, and neck, so you can rotate the legs and arms when adding and removing doll’s clothing, and turn her head side to side during play. She’s 14” long and weighs about 1lb. 5 ounces.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 25, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just How I Remember
reviews.reviewText: For my 10th birthday, my parents gave me some money, took me to Walmart, and let me pick some toys. This was one of two, and together they were my Favorite. Babies. Ever. Well, about 2 years afterward, it came up missing (I still have the orher one.) It was nowhere. The rooms have been cleaned out multiple times, and my parents knew how much I loved it, nevertheless, it was gone. I thought about this baby doll for years since. Now I'm 18, and at 1am I did some digging and found the doll on Google, and after cross examination with Amazon, found it. The clothes were lighter than before, now being a pale pink whereas before they were hot pink, and the top on the old one was an actual top, where this one was a tie. However, the doll looks exactly the same, feels the same, same size, whole thing. Thank you for still having this doll

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars SO Realistic And CHEAP!! 😍
reviews.reviewText: I have always wanted a reborn baby, and most of them are so expensive, and hard to find. This reborn baby was super cheap for my budget and so BEAUTIFUL! It’s hand painted- and has realistic details! I bought the boy, and I’m obsessed! 💕 It is atomically correct with not the squishiest body. It is vinyl but not very squishy. The limbs can move up and down, he is in a curled position. 😇 He/She comes with a pacifier, baby blanket, outfit, bottle and certificate of adoption. 100% giftable, and value for money! 💗

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2015
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars It looks like a boy's thing
reviews.reviewText: My Grandaughter loves her. I think she is cute, precious. I would give it a 5 star, except, I was aware she a was anatomically doll, but was totally shocked when we saw the belly button. It looks like a boy's thing. My Grandaughter asked why it looked that way. Her parents were not sure if they would let her keep it, because of this. She is seven. We explained to her that sometimes newborns belly buttons can look like this, she has to keep the white strip over it. So please in the future, consider one that doesn't look like this. This is the second doll I bought for her, the first one was a mini, just adorable. We are greatly satisfied with her, even the girl part, but not the belly button. I am planning on buying more jc dolls, as they are the best I found that look real, and your company is very helpful, friendly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 7, 2016
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very cute, very detailed, very perfect.
reviews.reviewText: Normally I wait a few days before reviewing a doll so I've had time to live with it and get a real opinion, but I can't imagine my opinion changing. I adore this doll. It is extremely detailed and has an adorable expression that can melt hearts. It is made of fairly solid vinyl, so it isn't what I would call cuddly, but since that isn't why I got it, I'm fine with that.Preemie sized baby clothes fits it fairly well, though those clothes are a bit on the long side. It won't fit perfectly, but the preemie sized stuff I have for my other dolls fits it well enough.I'm not a fan of the clothes it comes in. They doesn't seem to fit the doll very well and just isn't to my liking, but since I prefer to change my doll's clothes (I collect various types of semi-realistic dolls), that doesn't bother me and isn't worth knocking a star off since the doll itself is everything I expected and wanted.It definitely looks better in real life than in the provided pictures here on Amazon. I may be able to add pictures in a few days, once I get them off my camera.This doll is a very good addition to my collection and I think anyone who wants a small (14 inch) full bodied doll would be very pleased with this one. I certainly couldn't be more pleased with my purchase.
